大卫·阿奎特（David Arquette）的杜威（Dewey）将在“尖叫7”中返回https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-arquettes-dewey-will-return-return-in-scream-7-3843676?utm_source = rss＆source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = david-arquret-arquett-arquettes-deweyey-will-retream-retern-77Surej Singh Wed, 05 Mar 2025 06:03:57 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3843676 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/scream-david-arquette@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/scream-david-arquette@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/scream-david-arquette@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/scream-david-arquette@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/scream-david-arquette@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/scream-david-arquette@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/scream-david-arquette@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>角色死于2022年的“尖叫”</p><p>大卫·阿奎特（David Arquette）的杜威（David Arquette）的杜威（Dewey）将首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-arquettes-dewey-will-return-in-scream-7-3843676">“ Scream 7”中</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/scream-david-arquette@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/scream-david-arquette@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/scream-david-arquette@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/scream-david-arquette@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/scream-david-arquette@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/scream-david-arquette@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/scream-david-arquette@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-arquette">戴维·阿奎特（David Arquette</a> ）的杜威·莱利（Dewey Riley）将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/scream"><em>尖叫7</em></a>中卷土重来。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/scream-6-review-ghostface-jenna-ortega-3409588">“ Scream VI”评论：穿越从未睡过的城市的噩梦般的刺激</a></strong></li></ul><p>根据<a href="https://deadline.com/2025/03/david-arquette-scream-7-return-1236310976/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>截止日期的</em></a>报告，阿奎特（Arquette）的角色 - 在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/scream-review-horror-reboot-courteney-cox-3136061">2022年的软启动<em>尖叫</em>中被杀（也称为<em>Scream 5</em> ）</a> - 将在Meta Slasher电影中返回即将到来的第七部分。</p><p><em>截止日期</em>报告说，虽然杜威·莱利（Dewey Riley）将返回，但围绕电影情节的细节以及角色将如何恢复（如果有的话）被保密。据报道，杜威·莱利（Dewey Riley）将是三个死者的角色之一，被带回<em>尖叫7</em> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3823659" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3823659" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3823659" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Parker-Courteney-David.jpg" alt="帕克·波西（Parker Posey），考特尼·考克斯（Courteney Cox）和大卫·阿奎特（David Arquette）在“尖叫2”中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Parker-Courteney-David.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Parker-Courteney-David-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Parker-Courteney-David-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Parker-Courteney-David-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Parker-Courteney-David-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Parker-Courteney-David-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3823659" class="wp-caption-text">帕克·波西（Parker Posey），考特尼·考克斯（Courteney Cox）和大卫·阿奎特（David Arquette）在“尖叫2”中图片来源：约瑟夫·维尔斯（Joseph Viles）维度通过盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>最近，据报道，扮演Stu Macher的Matthew Lillard（两个原始的Ghostface杀手之一） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/matthew-lillard-reportedly-returning-for-scream-7-3833398">将返回Scream 7</a> ，尽管他的角色大概在第一部电影的结尾被杀害。</p><p>如果Arquette的回归得到确认，他将标志着原始<em>尖叫</em>电影中的第三位主角回来<em>尖叫7</em> ，跟随<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/neve-campbell-returns-scream-melissa-barrera-sacking-3600529">Neve Campbell</a>和Courteney Cox的脚步，后者是Arquette的现实生活中的前妻。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/courteney-cox-officially-set-to-return-for-scream-7-3823653">确认考克斯的回归</a>后，她表示希望以某种方式，杜威的角色将被带回即将上映的第七部电影。</p><p> <em>Scream 7</em>目前定于2026年2月27日发布。</p><p> <em>Scream 7</em>在生产中遇到了一些困难。它受到WGA和SAG-AFTRA罢工的影响，而原始导演 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/scream-7-director-christopher-landon-quits-project-3562999">克里斯托弗·兰登（Christopher Landon）在2023年结束了他参与电影</a>。</p><p>首席女演员梅利莎·巴雷拉（Melissa Barrera） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/fans-vow-to-boycott-scream-vii-after-melissa-barrera-is-dropped-over-israel-hamas-war-post-3546483">在支持巴勒斯坦的Instagram上发布</a>后，于2023年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/fans-vow-to-boycott-scream-vii-after-melissa-barrera-is-dropped-over-israel-hamas-war-post-3546483">从<i>尖叫的7</i>中脱颖而出</a>。她讨论了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/melissa-barrera-felt-lonely-and-scared-after-scream-firing-3619100">被解雇后感到“孤独和害怕”</a> ，但也说她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/melissa-barrera-says-she-is-at-peace-with-scream-7-firing-3576595">对它的发展“和平”</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3384124" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3384124" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3384124" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Scream_Barrera_Ortega.jpg" alt="尖叫" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Scream_Barrera_Ortega.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Scream_Barrera_Ortega-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Scream_Barrera_Ortega-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Scream_Barrera_Ortega-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Scream_Barrera_Ortega-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Scream_Barrera_Ortega-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3384124" class="wp-caption-text"> Melissa Barrera和Jenna Ortega在“ Scream VI”中。信用：最重要的</figcaption></figure><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jenna-ortega-will-not-be-returning-to-the-scream-franchise-3546990">大约在同一时间宣布，珍娜·奥尔特加（Jenna Ortega）也不会返回</a>，这是因为安排了她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>系列<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/wednesday"><em>周三的</em></a>冲突以及薪资纠纷。</p><p>但是，在该系列中扮演西德尼·普雷斯科特（Sidney Prescott）的尼夫·坎贝尔（Neve Campbell）将在2023年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/scream-6-review-ghostface-jenna-ortega-3409588"><em>Scream 6</em></a>中脱颖而出后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/neve-campbell-says-she-was-sad-to-miss-last-scream-film-as-she-opens-up-about-return-3761903">重新扮演自己的角色</a>。梅森·古丁（Mason Gooding）也将随着乍得·米克斯（Chad Meeks-Martin）的身份返回，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/scream-7-to-introduce-new-generation-with-sidneys-daughter-cast-3815173">伊莎贝尔·梅（Isabel May）将扮演西德尼（Sidney）的女儿</a>。安娜·坎普（Anna Camp）也宣布，新来者包括Celeste O&#39;Connor，Asa Germann， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/mckenna-grace-scoliosis-interview-music-ghostbusters-surgery-3350158">McKenna Grace</a>和Sam Rechner。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/scream-vi"><em>Scream 6</em></a>获得了 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/scream-6-review-ghostface-jenna-ortega-3409588">四星级评论</a>，Alex Flood撰写了<em>NME</em> ：“ <em>Scream VI</em>并不完美：持续的元参考（过去的杀手，特许经营权的“规则”）在去年的重新启动中感到有创造力，但在这里变得累人。山姆被压抑的愿望模仿她的父亲（Billy Loomis，原始的Ghostface）也有一个令人困惑的子图，她出现在幻觉中，告诉她谋杀人们。参加通常的展示会议，使观众保持最新状态，但让它感觉像Z Z gen <em>poirot</em> ，这一切都可能开始让您感到紧张。幸运的是，这是您所忙于注意的事情的纯粹，流血的喜悦。也许更多的恐怖坏人<em>应该</em>搬到纽约？”</p><p>大卫·阿奎特（David Arquette）的杜威（David Arquette）的杜威（Dewey）将首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-arquettes-dewey-will-return-in-scream-7-3843676">“ Scream 7”中</a>。</p> ;
