 Vince Neil为医疗程序做准备https://www.nme.com/news/music/motley-crue-postpone-las-vegas-vegas-vegas-vesidency-asidency-as-vince-neil-prepares-for-medical-precedure-3843651?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = motley-crue-postpone-las-vegas-vegas-sisidency-as-as vince-nneil-neil-prepares for Medical-ProcedureSurej Singh Wed, 05 Mar 2025 03:27:05 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music NewsMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3843651 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vince-neil-motley-crue@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vince-neil-motley-crue@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vince-neil-motley-crue@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vince-neil-motley-crue@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vince-neil-motley-crue@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vince-neil-motley-crue@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vince-neil-motley-crue@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>三月和四月的演出将于9月举行</p><p>文<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/motley-crue-postpone-las-vegas-residency-as-vince-neil-prepares-for-medical-procedure-3843651">斯·尼尔（Vince Neil）为医疗程序做准备时，莫特利·克鲁（MötleyCrüe）后拉斯维加斯（Las Vegas）的住院医师</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vince-neil-motley-crue@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vince-neil-motley-crue@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vince-neil-motley-crue@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vince-neil-motley-crue@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vince-neil-motley-crue@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vince-neil-motley-crue@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/vince-neil-motley-crue@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/motley-crue">莫特利·克鲁（MötleyCrüe）</a>宣布将其拉斯维加斯居住地推迟，因为主持人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/vince-neil">文斯·尼尔（Vince Neil）</a>准备接受“必需的医疗程序”  - 在下面了解更多信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/motley-crue-interview-dogs-of-war-nikki-sixx-john-5-new-album-3751277">莫特利·克鲁（MötleyCrüe</a></strong></li></ul><p>乐队将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/motley-crue-announce-2025-las-vegas-residency-3799512">3月28日至4月19日在Park MGM的Dolby Live举行11场演出</a>。但是，乐队昨晚（3月4日）上了社交媒体，告知粉丝们，这些节目将于9月重新安排。</p><p>这11场演出现在将在9月12日至10月3日之间举行，所有先前购买的节目都在新近重新安排的演出中受到尊敬的<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fmotley-crue-tickets%2Fartist%2F910417" target="_blank" rel="noopener">所有节目 - 您可以在此处找到剩余的门票</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3562954" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3562954" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3562954" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/motley-crue-cancel-new-years-eve-show.jpg" alt="Nikki Sixx与Motley Crue一起表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/motley-crue-cancel-new-years-eve-show.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/motley-crue-cancel-new-years-eve-show-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/motley-crue-cancel-new-years-eve-show-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/motley-crue-cancel-new-years-eve-show-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/motley-crue-cancel-new-years-eve-show-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/motley-crue-cancel-new-years-eve-show-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3562954" class="wp-caption-text"> Vince Neil和Nikki Sixx于2023年11月14日在澳大利亚墨尔本与MötleyCrüe一起在Marvel Stadium演出</figcaption></figure><p>这位歌手在谈到文斯·尼尔（Vince Neil）必须进行的“必需的医疗程序”时说：“对于所有期待今年春季见到我们的克鲁黑德（Crüeheads），我真的很抱歉。我的健康是我的头等大事，因此我可以为您带来您应得的出色表演，我迫不及待想回到舞台上。感谢您对我的所有良好祝愿。您的支持意味着超出您所知道的。”</p><p>他的乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nikki-sixx">Nikki Sixx</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tommy-lee">Tommy Lee</a>和John 5在一份共同的声明中说：“请与我们一起希望Vince快速康复。我们期待他再次变得健康，并在9月接管拉斯维加斯。”</p><p>文斯·尼尔（Vince Neil）医疗程序的确切性质目前尚不清楚，但医生建议。在下面查看乐队的完整声明和拉斯维加斯居住期的新列表。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGykIAKS-Qc/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBo