绿日在“郊区耶稣”表演期间嘲笑美国副总统JD Vance https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-mock-us-vice-president-jd-vance-dance-durance-during-jesus-jesus-suburbia-performance-3843648?u？ tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = green-day-mock-us-vice-vice-vice-vice-jd-jd-vance-jd-vance-jesus-jesus-jesus-jesus of-buburbia-cormformanceSurej Singh Wed, 05 Mar 2025 02:45:13 +0000 Music NewsNewsPoliticsPunkRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3843648 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/green-day-jd-vance@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/green-day-jd-vance@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/green-day-jd-vance@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/green-day-jd-vance@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/green-day-jd-vance@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/green-day-jd-vance@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/green-day-jd-vance@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队在最近的演出中击败了埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）和唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-mock-us-vice-president-jd-vance-during-jesus-of-suburbia-performance-3843648">绿日后嘲笑美国副总统在“郊区耶稣”表演期间</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/green-day-jd-vance@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/green-day-jd-vance@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/green-day-jd-vance@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/green-day-jd-vance@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/green-day-jd-vance@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/green-day-jd-vance@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/green-day-jd-vance@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">绿日</a>在最近在澳大利亚举行的一场音乐会上嘲笑了美国副总统JD Vance。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/10-albums-that-wouldnt-exist-without-green-days-dookie-768209">没有绿色日的“ Dookie”，这10张专辑将不存在</a></strong></li></ul><p>在3月1日，乐队最近在澳大利亚墨尔本举行的音乐会上，绿日在JD Vance击中，JD Vance目前担任<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普总统</a>的第二次指挥。在音乐会上，乐队表演了精确的“ dookie”和“美国白痴”专辑。</p><p>在布景的“美国白痴”部分，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-joe-armstrong">比利·乔·阿姆斯特朗（Billie Joe Armstrong</a> and Co）。首先在冠军歌曲中召集唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的政府，将歌词“<em>我不是乡下人议程的一部分</em>”换成“<em>我不是Maga议程的一部分</em>”。乐队已经做了很多次， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-hit-out-at-donald-trump-during-new-years-rockin-eve-performance-3564375">可以追溯到2023年底</a>。</p><p>但是，3月1日在墨尔本举行的演出使他们鞭打了新的歌词，这次是针对副总统JD Vance。在表演“郊区耶稣”时，绿日从“<em>我智障或我刚好高兴？</em> ”“<em>我是智障还是我只是JD Vance？</em> ”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DGy64MVyXTL/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div 