" alt="Mudd的Wes Scantlin的水坑。信用 - 保罗·阿库莱塔（Paul Archuleta）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Puddle-of-Mudds-Wes-Scantlin.-Credit-Paul-Archuleta.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Puddle-of-Mudds-Wes-Scantlin.-Credit-Paul-Archuleta-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Puddle-of-Mudds-Wes-Scantlin.-Credit-Paul-Archuleta-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Puddle-of-Mudds-Wes-Scantlin.-Credit-Paul-Archuleta-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Puddle-of-Mudds-Wes-Scantlin.-Credit-Paul-Archuleta-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Puddle-of-Mudds-Wes-Scantlin.-Credit-Paul-Archuleta-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/puddle-of-mudd">Mudd的Wes Scantlin的水坑</a>声称他在周末在Daytona Bike Week举行的灾难性演出之前被他的前伴侣“屋顶”。</p><p>作为自行车周的一部分，摇滚乐队正在周六（3月1日）在佛罗里达州的Broken Skoke Saloon举行的福利表演。然而，该乐队的成员是免费的，乐队的成员签署了一把吉他，可以在演出中拍卖 - 然后是由一名投标人购买的，该竞标者为该乐器支付了5000美元，这笔钱用于儿童癌症研究。</p><p>但是，根据<a href="https://loudwire.com/puddle-of-mudd-wes-scantlin-claims-roofied-disastrous-2025-performance/"><em>Loudwire</em></a>的说法，与会者报道了该节目的几个问题，从Sound到Scantlin的一般舞台存在 - 据称他在绊倒和漫步时摇摇欲坠。</p><p>然而，斯坎特林声称他是由他的前乐队成员贝斯手肖恩·萨蒙（Sean Sammon）“屋顶”的。第二天，Scantlin接触了一位粉丝，向他询问了该节目，并将互动拍摄并<a href="https://www.facebook.com/reel/1339893600487686" target="_blank" rel="noopener">发布到Facebook</a> 。他在视频中说：“我很烂，我很烂……但是我被屋顶了。”</p><p>斯坦特林继续说：“我的老贝斯手肖恩·萨蒙（Sean Sammon）昨晚把我屋顶了，所以他可以操他的屁股。”然后，他将两个中指放在相机上，然后走开，然后转过身来再伸出一根中指。</p><p> <em>NME</em>已与Sammon联系以进行评论。 </p><figure id="attachment_3038667" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3038667" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3038667" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Puddle-Of-Mudd-Wes-Scantlin.jpg" alt="泥泞的水坑" width="2000" height="1269" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Puddle-Of-Mudd-Wes-Scantlin.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Puddle-Of-Mudd-Wes-Scantlin-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Puddle-Of-Mudd-Wes-Scantlin-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Puddle-Of-Mudd-Wes-Scantlin-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Puddle-Of-Mudd-Wes-Scantlin-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Puddle-Of-Mudd-Wes-Scantlin-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3038667" class="wp-caption-text"> Mudd Puddle的Wes Scantlin。图片来源：Brigitte Engl/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>演出结束后，Mudd音乐会的一些与会者感到失望， <a href="https://www.facebook.com/BrokenSpokeSaloon/posts/1043424371151437?ref=embed_post" target="_blank" rel="noopener">场地社交媒体页面</a>的评论在很大程度上对表演产生了负面影响。一个人写道：“我很高兴那是一场免费演出。” “如果我花钱看那个可怕的表演，我会很生气。</p><p>去年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/puddle-of-mudd-frontman-wes-scantlin-arrested-and-pepper-sprayed-after-police-stand-off-3780789">据报道，斯坎特林在警察对峙后被捕并喷了胡椒</a>。这位音乐家此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/puddle-mudd-singer-arrested-gun-charges-2139509">因涉嫌试图用枪登机而于2017年</a>被捕。</p><p>在其他消息中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/puddle-of-mudds-wes-scantlin-admits-infamous-nirvana-cover-looked-and-sounded-like-total-shit-3369672">斯坎特林承认穆德臭名昭著的涅rv床的封面“看上去和听起来像是狗屎”。</a></p><p> Mudd的Wes Scantlin的Puddle声称，在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>首次出现<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/puddle-of-mudds-wes-scantlin-claims-he-was-roofied-by-ex-bandmate-before-disastrous-gig-3843634">灾难性演出之前，他被前伴侣“屋顶”</a> 。</p> ;
